items.title: Teamsters begin 'largest strike' against Amazon
items.description: The Teamsters said the strike will begin Thursday at several facilities, including in New York City, Atlanta, California and Illinois.

items.title: Southwestern Democrats throw support behind Ken Martin for DNC chair
items.description: Four state party chairs are backing Minnesota's Ken Martin in his bid to chair the Democratic National Committee (DNC), ABC News has learned.
